{"tid":1699690,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[急要!!] 有冇諗過全民一齊偷裝多啲cctv監警?","createTime":"2019-11-08T06:28:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T06:47:26.000Z","uid":107157,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e28f3aadfeb2b6dd8ef6f9b0f1f8b8fce88d0b47","tid":1699690,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:28:58.000Z","msg":"已經太多案件因為冇cctv或者角度唔適合而不了了之，咩都告唔入。<br />\n<br />\n建議全民齊裝cam，<br />\n買啲充電式CCTV搵隱蔽位周街裝。<br />\n啲狗做咩事都無所遁形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n近狗屋既裝，高位裝，近海裝，空地裝，甚至屋企裝監視屋外情況。<br />\n裝完映相作証，事後比人拆左就証明到比大家知道死因絕對有可疑。<br />\n<br />\n仲有咩高招請賜教。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想再有人被自殺就同我推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a7b7fd7cde772f4c15cff056b8b5765fe266d0","tid":1699690,"uid":8477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:30:49.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黑警為所欲為<br />\n港人反抗自衛</strong></span></span></div>"},{"pid":"d1b0e2162e5f4cd3046b03256aaafd523702a15d","tid":1699690,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:31:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ddb433e157fb6e9fa677dcf05bf9fef5c592c7f","tid":1699690,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:32:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">全民監警，刻不容緩</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"dbde191898cced6f447c3bb3a684f33787dc2f4a","tid":1699690,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:33:16.000Z","msg":"自推 2/2"},{"pid":"eac350d9a32a4079fbc03bdf59384805383919ad","tid":1699690,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci